IX. BUDGET NARRATIVE

1. Personnel

Includes salaries and fringe for:

• WHNP — $145,000
• CNM — $165,000
• OB/GYN provider
• Addictionologist
• Psychiatrist/PMHNP
• RNs (24/7)
• Therapists
• Case managers
• Residential supervisors
• Peer support specialists
• Education & workforce staff
• Administrative staff


2. Fringe Benefits

Covers health insurance, payroll taxes, retirement, and mandatory benefits.

3. Travel

Covers mileage for court appearances, hospital coordination, and statewide outreach.

4. Equipment

Includes medical equipment, fetal monitors, laptops/tablets for credentialing, and EHR hardware.

5. Supplies

Includes prenatal supplies, midwifery equipment (birthing tubs, dopplers), educational materials, parenting curriculum, and therapeutic supplies.

6. Contractual

Covers pharmacy partnership, laboratory services, and credentialing program fees.

7. Other

Covers facility lease, utilities, food services, transportation, insurance, and security.

8. Indirect Costs

Supports organizational infrastructure, finance, HR, and IT.

