---

XI. CONCLUSION

Open Arms provides a comprehensive, trauma‑informed, midwifery‑inclusive residential model that stabilizes pregnant women, prevents newborn foster care placements, and promotes long‑term family stability. Federal support will expand access to critical maternal and behavioral health services and strengthen outcomes across Louisiana.

